&gt; =\r\nan auxiliary to the knowledge of it. The sruti says: =C3=A2When to him &lt;br&gt;=\r\n\n&gt; everything has become the Self, who should see what and through what =\r\n&lt;br&gt;\n&gt; should one see?=C3=A2 etc. This nullifies the meaning of actions =\r\nin one who &lt;br&gt;\n&gt; has knowledge.&lt;br&gt;\n&gt;&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;/p&gt;\n\n    &lt;/div&gt;\n    =\r\n \n\n\n\n\n&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n\n    &lt;/div&gt;\n     \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n\n\n\n&lt;/div&gt;=\r\n&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;\r\n--0-2121644821-1308697751=:38466--\r\n\n"}}